<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜来到儿童中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都在转呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天又转呼啦圈吗？” 尼娜兴奋地问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪不太舒服。她今天在家。” 雪莉老师告诉尼娜，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还要用呼啦圈，但是，是另一种方法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜脱下背包，坐在波比和伊坦中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着贾森笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快要到圣诞节了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有谁家里已经做了装饰？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在前院放了圣诞灯饰。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在烛台上放了蜡烛。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们摆好了圣诞树，用灯装饰！” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“灯和蜡烛都很漂亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我最喜欢的装饰是用灯做的花环。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她给大家看一张发光的花环的照片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>花环是用灯做的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！我希望这里也有一个那样的花环。” 尼娜小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们马上就会有了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师推出一个呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜从来没有看过这么大的呼啦圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！莉琪不在真是太可惜了！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这会成为我们的花环吗？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！我们要把灯缠在上面。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师打开一个盒子，拿出一条灯串。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用胶带把一端贴在呼啦圈上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>剩下的缠在呼啦圈上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做好以后，连上另一条灯串，继续缠！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家努力把灯串缠到呼啦圈上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，所有盒子里的灯串都用完了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我都看不到呼啦圈了！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们给花环插电吧。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！” 孩子们欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在太空一定也能看到！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里怎么关灯了？” 弗拉尼校长把头伸进来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到了花环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真漂亮！这是你们做的吗？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。” 尼娜开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师看上去也很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道该把这个花环放在哪里！” 弗拉尼校长说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放在我们学校前面！怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>校长看着尼娜、波比、伊坦和贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦咧嘴笑了。“太好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真棒。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是不是少了一个人？” 弗拉尼校长问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪今天生病在家。” 尼娜说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但她一定也会同意的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们把花环抬到校门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师插了电。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪地上反射出温暖的灯光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜想快点给莉琪看看这个大花环。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>